title: LF Supp Main To Duo With Next Season
body:
Currently Silver 3 and was a Jungle main in Season 5, with Mid my go to! Currently in Pre-Season playing a lot of ADC and think with a good supp have the capability to climb with it. I still play Jungle and Mid quite a bit but slowly progressing towards ADC and would like a Support main to practice with in Pre-Season and climb in Season 6/Pre-Season!
IGN: iScorpion
Currently Playing/Doing A Great Job With: Tristana, Vayne, Lucian, Kalista, Corki and Sivir.

replies.body: gold 5 support main, been looking for a duo partner for awhile, add me if u want to
silver 3 sup mian here if you want to duo :)
Sure - add me in game if you would like some freelos
